# QA Wolf Take-Home — Hacker News /newest Sort Check

Validates that **exactly** the first 100 posts on [Hacker News → /newest](https://news.ycombinator.com/newest) are sorted **newest → oldest** using **JavaScript + Playwright (Chromium)**.

---

## Quick Start

```bash
# install deps
npm i
# install Playwright browsers (one-time)
npx playwright install
# run
npm start
# or
node index.js
